chart_description: This chart shows the length of the largest external delivery queue for messages waiting to be sent from the exchange. A large queue length can indicate congestion or issues with message delivery.

dimension_descriptions.high: Number of messages waiting in the queue that have a high priority
dimension_descriptions.low: Number of messages waiting in the queue that have a low priority
dimension_descriptions.none: Number of messages waiting in the queue that do not have a priority
dimension_descriptions.normal: Number of messages waiting in the queue that have a normal priority
